   "source": [
    "- Tuples – Immutability\n",
    "- Tuple = immutable list → cannot change after creation\n",
    "- No add/remove/update: t[0] = 10 ❌\n",
    "- Defined using () → t = (1, 2, 3)\n",
    "- Read-only, but can access like list: t[0]"
   ]
